data.description: The most welcoming of floorplans awaits in Waterlefe - the area's only Golf and Boating Community!  The Jacaranda is an entertainers dream and this one is loaded with recent updates! Freshly repainted exterior and paver lanai just levelled, sanded and sealed enhance the outdoor living style as we enter "season".  Kitchen remodel highlighted by hand selected quartz counters, newer bedroom and den flooring with a 2021 HVAC and 2023 Water Heater.  A transferrable Home Tech Warranty also covers your appliances and more.  So much to love here and waiting for you to add your own personal flavor to it. Soaring ceilings in the Open Concept great room is exactly what you've been looking for in Manatee County's original Resort Style Community.  More than a neighborhood, Waterlefe Residents have access to many options...centered around the Waterlefe River Club with new updates (9/23) featuring a Restaurant, Bar, Fitness Center, Meeting Space, Tiki Bar and Jr Olympic Pool - the heartbeat of the neighborhood! Imagine days with friends at daily fitness classes, card games, social functions, book clubs and more - your social calendar is full! Golf Club Membership as well as Marina Slips are available yet optional (the course has re-opened to rave reviews and the golf clubhouse is undergoing renovation currently) Phenomenal Cable TV, WIFI and Internet INCLUDED in HOA fees - Landscaping package is part of homeownership here as well. Come see the home in person and you'll know why this will be your new Waterlefe Home - CDD included in taxes
